Name: Overchunked
About the game: Overchunked is a game about a giant circular saw constantly moving forward: steer it left and right to guide its course, dodge obstacles, TNT explosives and destroy the rest of the environment to obtain points! FAST GAMEPLAY: easy to play hard to master DESTRUCTION IS SATISFACTION: destroy everything on your path and avoid obstacles EVERCHANGING WORLD: enjoy the dynamic procedurally generated map VIVID: bright and eye-catching colors WORLD LADDER: compete with the online leaderboard MUSIC: original soundtrack both funky and soothing ZEN MODE: no obstacles, no score. Pure relax! ATOMIC STUFF: unlock and enable insane post-processing filters
